subject: Football
lead_paragraph: BALTIMORE, Nov. 18 (AP) — The Cleveland Browns actually had to come back onto the field Sunday to complete a 33-30 overtime victory against the Baltimore Ravens after it appeared the game ended with a missed field goal by Phil Dawson.
